sections.text: district, defined.Residential district shall mean the territory contiguous to and including a highway not comprising a business district when the property on such highway for a distance of three hundred feet or more is in the main improved with residences or residences and buildings in use for business.SourceLaws 1993, LB 370, ยง 150.
